name: To the Moon - Shiba Inu Supremacy
description: [ENG] - With the high use of Shiba Inu puppies in the world of cryptocurrencies, I felt impacted to create an art symbolizing all the euphoria of the current market. [PT/BR] - Com a alta do uso dos cachorrinhos Shiba Inu no mundo de criptomoedas, me senti impactado a criar uma arte simbolizando toda a euforia do mercado atual.
